The '''Council of Ithorian Elders''' was the ruling body of [[Ithor/Legends|Ithor]]. [[Momaw Nadon/Legends|Momaw Nadon]] was tried before the Council after surrendering their agricultural secrets to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Following the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] the council was reconvened by surviving [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorians]] that were abroad during the [[Species/Legends|species']] homeworld's destruction.

